{"tid":2356673,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拉林卓廷阻拍攝 警爆楊雪盈議辦","createTime":"2021-01-07T03:12:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T07:18:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"378bbb0f0919c5c9a0d9fbd9d98e2388b370bf4f","tid":2356673,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T03:12:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210107/GPV2235BARCNTHJFFW6PHAORLE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210107%2FGPV2235BARCNTHJFFW6PHAORLE%2F&d=tgCcTb3Ji4LFIEkqsM1g5iPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=d14dbc8e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210107%2FGPV2235BARCNTHJFFW6PHAORLE%2F&h=fa442976\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210107/GPV2235BARCNTHJFFW6PHAORLE/</a><br />\n<br />\n拉林卓廷阻拍攝 警爆楊雪盈議辦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9WxUx9kYTjj1vFv8Wa9bLqmyndk=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/U7EUE2WZXFDYBA4HGMA4E3AWOM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9WxUx9kYTjj1vFv8Wa9bLqmyndk%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FU7EUE2WZXFDYBA4HGMA4E3AWOM.jpg&h=8a485f40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■楊雪盈被捕後稱發燒需送院；其議辦遭警方爆閘（圓圖）搜查。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警察國安處昨大舉拘捕民主派人士，包括前立法會議員林卓廷、區議員伍健偉及楊雪盈等人，均透過fb公佈消息及直播被捕過程，但被警員阻止拍攝，並警告或涉阻差辦公。林被警察鎖手銬帶上車時寄語：「大家加油！」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：國安歹毒：初選有罪  警拘戴耀廷53人<br />\n稱拍片或涉阻差<br />\n<br />\n已多番被捕的林卓廷昨再被拘捕，其fb片段所見，西九龍總區重案組2A隊探員清晨登門時，探員對有人在場拍攝顯得不耐煩稱：「兩位人士，𠵱家警方行動進行當中，麻煩你停止錄影」，又警告拍攝者或涉阻差辦公。林之後被帶到地區辦事處搜查。<br />\n<br />\n元朗區議員伍健偉亦在fb直播被捕，片中便衣警指他去年參與初選活動，在於達成戴耀廷在《蘋果日報》及各大媒體上提倡的「攬炒香港十部曲計劃」，志在嚴重干擾阻撓破壞香港特別行政區政權機關依法履行職能。伍被扣留調查，又透過fb說「願粹我命，捍衛我城，全民自救，打破宿命」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：陷獄黃之鋒首涉國安罪  與還柙快必隨時再被捕<br />\n<br />\n灣仔區議會主席楊雪盈亦直播被捕過程，同樣有女警要求拍攝者停止攝影，「如果唔係我哋會拘捕你」。楊之後更新消息指「辦事處鐵閘已被爆」，後被押往搜查，其後她因發燒及身體不適，被送院診治。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局員工陣線則在fb宣布：「警方國安處今早以國安法拘捕最少50人，多名民主派人士被捕，其中包括本會主席余慧明。」據知，余昨晨約6時被捕，警方持搜查令，將她及家人電腦沒收。新民主同盟范國威則於清晨6時許，於fb指正被捕，「罪名係參加初選」，至7時許他身穿西裝，雙手被鎖上手銬進入將軍澳警署。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/a0A6RxsxVCxy6hTY9xzGYE21YLc=/1276x557/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FFWVDISNBBBLLC2UZU3AQAHLSE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fa0A6RxsxVCxy6hTY9xzGYE21YLc%3D%2F1276x557%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFFWVDISNBBBLLC2UZU3AQAHLSE.gif&h=64fc4109&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■左起尹兆堅、李予信、徐子見等多人被帶署扣查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/gOx6ff6DuTwV8owXR3eEA1JNuOE=/1565x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QTQXSNT3IZBGZNQGUNLFKXQMWI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgOx6ff6DuTwV8owXR3eEA1JNuOE%3D%2F1565x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQTQXSNT3IZBGZNQGUNLFKXQMWI.jpg&h=5ecbd70b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警員（左）昨晨登門拘捕林卓廷，又警告在場拍攝者或涉阻差辦公。林卓廷fb片段截圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HXgws4_g4xZgRpCu5s9LtQoVi4M=/2214x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CRCJKHBTBZGNJNC7ZNJROIXXRQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHXgws4_g4xZgRpCu5s9LtQoVi4M%3D%2F2214x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCRCJKHBTBZGNJNC7ZNJROIXXRQ.jpg&h=c3ae67fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■范國威遭鎖上手銬押至將軍澳警署。"},{"pid":"16d6bcca4ac39f0c57b3cee3f700937cff0f5fe1","tid":2356673,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T06:44:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec055c784f4aa060856bc6b260a2baf7c6af3139","tid":2356673,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T07:18:14.000Z","msg":"初選都顛覆國家，拍片應該算從事恐怖活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}